  	<body>
  		<div xml:id="pl-l2d13c1">
  			<head xml:id="pll2d13c1-Hd1e3513">Capitulum 1</head>
  			<head xml:id="pll2d13c1-Hd1e3516" type="questionTitle">De primo distinctionis opere</head>
  			<p xml:id="pll2d13c1-d1e3519">Prima autem distinctionis operatio fuit formatio lucis, sicut 
  				ostendit Scriptura, quae, commemorata rerum informitate, eorum 
  				dispositionem a luce inchoavit, subdens: 
  				<cit>
  					<quote xml:id="pll2d13c1-Qd1e3523" source="http://scta.info/resource/gen1_3"> <!-- 1:4 might also follow -->Dixit Deus: Fiat 
  						lux, et facta est lux, et divisit lucem a tenebris, appellavitque 
  						lucem diem, et tenebras noctem. Et factum est vespere et mane, 
  						dies unus</quote>
  					<bibl>Genesis 1:3 seqq.</bibl>
  				</cit>.
  				<cit>
  					<quote xml:id="pll2d13c1-Qd1e3534">Congrue mundi ornatus a luce incepit, une cetera, 
  						quae creanda erant, viderentur</quote>
  					<bibl>Glossa interlin. ad v. 3</bibl>
  				</cit>.
  			</p>
  		</div>
